ZH: 这家公司的老板横行霸道，员工都非常不满。
EN: The boss of this company is overbearing and employees are very unhappy.

ZH: 他在学校里横行霸道，经常欺负其他同学。
EN: He is overbearing at school and often bullies other students.

ZH: 那个政客横行霸道，只顾自己的利益。
EN: That politician is overbearing, only concerned about his own interests.

